	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema625_04_ih_0003">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="3_light_purple" lang="y">
					컴퍼스를 3 ㎝만큼 벌려서 그린 원의 원주를 몇 ㎝인지 구해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
					<div class="img_area">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_04_IH/0003_01.png" alt="" />
						<ul>
							<li>0</li>
							<li>1</li>
							<li>2</li>
							<li>3</li>
							<li>4</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="flex align_center gap_10">
